Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:31.17,1:45:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间可以吗？可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:34.11,1:45:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这边请
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:38.11,1:45:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好   下次见
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:44.12,1:45:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请    好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:54.13,1:45:57.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了   婶婶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:45:59.07,1:46:02.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天刚下班吗？
