Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:14.15,1:46:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:23.09,1:46:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不能讲出去唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:46:27.10,1:46:30.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢这样阿
