Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:29.09,1:48:32.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这边哟
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:38.16,1:48:41.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要帮你你拿上去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:43.10,1:48:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系   等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:48.17,1:48:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体还好吗？还好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:53.11,1:48:56.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比较能动了    太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:48:57.11,1:49:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次出国吗？对
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:01.12,1:49:04.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点紧张     应该可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:05.12,1:49:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有事就跟我讲    射谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:09.13,1:49:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:49:21.14,1:49:24.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我帮你吧
