Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:21.06,1:50:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:24.13,1:50:27.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去我那边吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:27.07,1:50:30.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:50:30.14,1:50:33.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我带着可以
