Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:35.14,1:51:38.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欧洲附近都很美吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:42.08,1:51:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你愿意的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:47.15,1:51:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出国就好好欣赏
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:51:51.15,1:51:54.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到处走走看看
